ZESTY LIMITED - USER CONDITIONS FOR USING THE WEBSITE

1. DEFINITIONS

In these conditions:

Database means the directory database of Health Professionals which you can obtain access to by using the Website;

Health Practice means the practice with which the Health Professional is associated in whatever legal form such practice takes and whether the Health Professional is a partner, employee, consultant or otherwise of that practice;

Health Professional means any health practitioner who is listed as such on the Website;

User or you means any person who uses the Website, including those who book an appointment using the Website but excluding the Health Professionals whose arrangement with us is governed by the "Health Professionals Conditions for Registration;"

Zesty.co.uk or Website means the website currently located at the URL www.zesty.co.uk or any similar such Website which is owned and operated by us and any other website we may own or run from time to time that links through to these conditions; and

Zesty, we, our or us means Zesty Limited, a company registered in England and Wales under number 08294659, whose registered office is at Tura, Kilmington Common, Warminster, Wiltshire, BA12 6QX.

2. INTRODUCTION

2.1. Zesty.co.uk allows you to search for Health Professionals and arrange appointment bookings with Health Professionals. It also allows you to assist in gathering information, posting opinions and ratings in relation to the Health Professionals and engaging in interactive health forums.

2.2. If you log-on to or use any part of the Website you agree to these conditions. If you do not want to agree to these conditions, do not log on to or use this Website.

2.3. We may change these conditions at any time without giving you express notice. Please check these conditions from time to time for any changes. By continuing to use the Website you agree to all the changes we make to these conditions.

3. ARRANGEMENTS WITH HEALTH PROFESSIONALS

3.1. Any contract for the provision of medical advice, assistance or procedure with any Health Professional or Health Practice listed on the Website is made directly between you and the Health Professional or Health Practice and we are not a party to that contract. In recognition of this, you acknowledge that any claim you may have that is in any way connected with a dispute you have with or a complaint against a Health Professional or Health Practice must be brought directly against that Health Professional or Health Practice and not against us.

3.2. We make no claims as to the quality, safety or legality of any of the Health Professionals listed. While we require the Health Professional to ensure the listing is truthful and accurate, we make no representations or warranties regarding any of the Health Professionals and cannot confirm the accuracy of the listings or their content. We do not own, inspect or provide content for any of the Health Professionals listed on our site.

3.3 It is the sole responsibility of the Health Professional to be eligible and capable of providing the appropriate medical advice, assistance or procedure.

3.4. You remain liable for any fees or costs or other liabilities that you incur with a Health Professional or Health Practice.

3.5. Please be aware that:

3.5.1. you use the Website at your own risk;

3.5.2. you should make sure you are satisfied with the exact type and nature of the services being offered by the Health Professionals you search for using the Website. We also recommend that you check the qualifications of the Health Professionals;

3.5.3. you should not rely on the Website for advice. You must always seek professional medical advice. In an emergency always telephone the emergency services; and

3.5.4. we cannot guarantee the accuracy of the results of any search made via the Website search tool.

